(309, 'Head office', 'head-office', '', '', 'The comprehensive network of agents of Hoang Ha allows a port to port service and door to door service, satisfying clients needs, and offering an effective control and follow up on all shipments at all time.', 'Head office', '<p>Company name:&nbsp;<strong>Hoang Ha International Logistics Joinstock company</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Trade name:&nbsp;<strong>HOANG HA INTERNATIONAL LOGISTICS</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Date of foundation: December, 04 1992</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Date of incorporation: December, 04 1992</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><img alt="Head office" src="http://hoangha.com/images/stories/chinhnhanh/hcm/HH_01.jpg" style="width: 300px; height: 338px; margin-left: 10px; margin-right: 10px; float: right;" />AGENT NETWORK</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The comprehensive network of agents of&nbsp;Hoang Ha&nbsp;allows a port to port service and door to door service, satisfying clients needs, and offering an effective control and follow up on all shipments at all time.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>DOMESTIC NETWORK</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Ho Chi Minh</li>\r\n	<li>Ha Noi Branch</li>\r\n	<li>Da Nang Branch</li>\r\n	<li>Can Tho Branch</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Add: Lot III-22, 19/5A Rd, Tan Binh IZ, Tan Phu Dist., Hochiminh City, Vietnam</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tel: (84.8) 3815 5319</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Fax: (84.8) 3815 5320</p>\r\n', 0, 1379940349, 'en', 1, ',3,13,'),
