(364, 'Mission', 'mission', '', '', '<p>We aim to be known as professional, efficient, reliable and friendly company to deal with.Value &amp; Vision</p>\r\n', 'Value & Vision', '<p align="LEFT" style="margin-left: -0.03cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 150%">We aim to be known as professional, efficient, reliable and friendly company to deal with.</p>\r\n\r\n<p align="LEFT" style="margin-left: -0.03cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 150%">We care about and highly value all our customer, no matter how different their requirements, products and expectations are. They all are our special clients each requiring an individual approach.</p>\r\n\r\n<p align="LEFT" style="margin-left: -0.03cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 150%">Our experienced staff are highly trained to help the customers to overcome all and every barrier, efficiently ensuring the prompt freight forwarding and timely cargo delivery services.</p>\r\n', 0, 1380547508, 'en', 1, ',2,'),
